title: Spliced Business Formations within 8 Quarters for Wisconsin (DISCONTINUED)
notes:
The Business Formation Statistics are now released on a monthly basis, and the quarterly series will no longer be updated. See BFSBF8QTOTALSAWI (https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/BFSBF8QTOTALSAWI) for an alternative.

This series combines (splices) https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/BF8QSAWI and https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/PBF8QSAWI to provide the entire time series for the actual and projected business formations within 8 quarters.
